      { "number": 16, "name": "Edouard MENDY",   "highlights": "Faced 11 shots, conceded 3. 62% save rate with 3 save-and-deflects. Kept Senegal competitive through the first hour." },
      { "number": 19, "name": "Moussa NIAKHATE", "highlights": "81 passes, 75 completed (93%). 20 line break attempts, 16 completed (80%). Dominant ball-playing CB, organiser of Senegal's build-up." },
